column5: Heres what Karls gonna be sending the winners of yesterdays contests...  2007 Extreme Angler Annual Magazine Nitro Bait Crappie or Trout Worms Eagle Claw Hooks Mizmo Tube Jigs RoadRunner Panfish Spinner Strike King Soft Plastics Snag Proof Frog Mepps/Williams or Lucky Strike Patch Matzuo Zandershad Twitchbait

The winners were:  vance Fishmaster Rich Clemens Bill Parker Gerritt fishinonthebrain lundboy bucktail walleyejigger irishfield Motorhead troutologist ccmtcanada
